{"by":"lynndotpy","id":47764958,"kids":[47770453],"parent":47760529,"text":"This is uncanny. Just yesterday, I was complaining about the state of photo editing software (Adobe and Google are no-gos, and Darkroom provided a thousand thorns). I wished that DaVinci had a photo editor, because I had similar pains about video editing that were resolved when I learned about DaVinci.<p>AND it runs on Linux!<p>It&#x27;s not every night you make a wish and wake up to find out it has come true.","time":1776170766,"type":"comment"}